{"id": 3125, "genre": 1000, "title": "你觉得线上社交用语里的情绪已经通货膨胀到什么地步了？", "description": "现实和网络上情绪汇率至少是 1:100。（题图来自：iStock ©️Aleksei Morozov）", "record_count": 8250, "comment_count": 19, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20200116225043qvTIRN91ZQDaLHOc.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2020-01-16T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 6193, "title": "你觉得线上社交用语里的情绪已经通货膨胀到什么地步了？", "content": "社交用语里的情绪已经通货膨胀到什么地步了？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 351858, "content": "现实中“哦”＝“嗯”，网络上“哦”＝“拜拜/呵呵”", "image": "img/option/option/20200116225407gA5IiYt4Dfybendm.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 351859, "content": "微笑甚至看起来欠打，起码得笑哭或者笑龇牙才可以", "image": "img/option/option/20200116225710vTz0po6lS3KIO8Bw.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 351860, "content": "四个以下“哈”约等于委婉“嗯哦行”，真开心起码得一排起步", "image": "img/option/option/20200116231117HVhXLdzCUQi7YW2A.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 351861, "content": "？已经很少单独出现表示疑问，而是打一排？？表示困惑", "image": "img/option/option/20200116230207I5fxmjsE81vFRM6J.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 351862, "content": "“嗯”＝“哦”；得“嗯嗯/嗯好”才勉强算“好的”", "image": "img/option/option/20200116230727BwFEhj2Iqz5yRdpa.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 351863, "content": "夸好还不够，得跟推销一样“我不允许周围有人不知道xxx”", "image": "img/option/option/20200116231335uwbEJqYQOp3C1nBm.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 351865, "content": "重要的事说一遍不行，还得说三遍", "image": "img/option/option/20200116231052PeV6m7jutDaiJzcH.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 351866, "content": "以前“笑死了”就够了，现在起码得“笑到头掉/邻居报警”", "image": "img/option/option/20200116231350ejE1WMqKBAsZd96J.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 351867, "content": "以上都没有／其他请在评论补充", "image": "img/option/option/202001162314054nJHFguv0MpbZzxf.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}